name: The Queen's Dreams: Coming Home
description:
Her feet did no touch the ground for her steps were too delicate for the earth.
Levitating with love she moved through this realm complete in the knowledge of what was achieved.
Peace.
Kindness.
Balance.
Respect.
She was here to console the hearts of those nursing the pain of loss.
She took each sadness and made it her own so that the holder could be free.
She was here for their healing.
The sign of change was her presence.
